<lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr- gẖmr ynạdy gẖmr ʿnd smạʿ ṣwtk fy ạlnhạr rḥmẗ fy
 ạllyl tsbyḥẗ wṣwtk yʿzy kl ạlbryẗ
