 ạkẖzy ạly ạldhr ạnt ạlnjạẗ
 ạmly fmy mn tsbyḥk ạlywm klẗ ybthj ạlqlb wạlʿmr ạlzy
 fdytẗ fạrnm lk bạlʿwd yạ qdws</lyrics>
<title>gẖmr ynạdy gẖmr</title>
